      • delete

        public boolean delete(java.lang.String word)
        Delete a given word from the Trie, verifying all four cases of deletion. Case 1 - The word is not on the Trie; Case 2 - The node where the word ends is a leaf; Case 3 - The node where the word ends is not a leaf; Case 4 - The node's parents have a fork
        Parameters:
        word - The word to be deleted from the Trie
        Returns:
        True if the word was deleted, false otherwise
